  "title": {"en": "Bitter gourd cultivation — DOA / HORDI recommendation"},
  "summary": {
    "en": "HORDI recommendation for bitter gourd (Momordica charantia) up to 1200 m. Planting seasons: Maha (Oct–Nov), Yala (Apr–May); year-round in favourable areas. Spacing 1.5 × 1 m, 3 seeds per hill, 6 kg seed/ha. Trellis three weeks post-planting. Yield 20–30 t/ha (OPV 20 t/ha, hybrid 20–30 t/ha)."
  },
